      • publishCommonEvent

        @Deprecated
void publishCommonEvent​(CommonEventData data,
                        CommonEventPublishInfo publishInfo,
                        ICommonEventSubscriber resultSubscriber)
                 throws RemoteException
        Deprecated. 
        Publishes a common event.
        Parameters:
        data - Indicates the CommonEventData object containing the common event content.
        publishInfo - Indicates the CommonEventPublishInfo object containing the common event attributes, such as the permission, user ID, and device ID.
        resultSubscriber - Indicates the last CommonEventSubscriber to receive the ordered common event. Generally, the current application is specified as the last subscriber to receive its own common event and obtain the common event publishing result.
        Throws:
        RemoteException - Throws this exception if an IPC exception occurs.
        Since:
        1
